"(1) (i) The early morning air over the rural tracks near the border was still cool and tinged with the scent of dew when Levi stood on the embankment, his breath visible in the faint light. The rhythmic chuff of a distant locomotive echoed through the vast, empty landscape, broken only by the occasional cry of a distant bird.\n(2) (i) As the sun’s first rays crept over the horizon, Levi glanced at his phone’s clock, uncertain if he should stay or return. He watched the slow crawl of a freight train rounding a bend ahead, its steel cars gleaming under the pale gold light. The monotony of the scene was shattered by a sudden, violent shudder that ran through the rails. Levi Rodriguez.\n(3) (i) A deafening roar erupted as the front of the lead engine lurches violently off the track. Metal shrieked and the ground trembled beneath Levi’s feet. He stumbled backward, heart pounding, as the remainder of the train twisted and toppled in a cascade of sparks and smoke.\n(4) (i) on , near . The catastrophic event unfolded before his eyes, leaving twisted wreckage and a cloud of acrid smoke that hung over the silent, shattered rails. Rajasthan. June 14, 2025. witnessed a train derailment."